				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-itzhak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7133855); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7133855&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226574" alt="Dr Itzhak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7133855)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-itzhak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7133855); return false;" >Dr Itzhak</a></span> <span class="odate time_1610192705 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">09 Jan 2021 11:45</span>
